  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>During the Single-Dose Period, the safety of oxymorphone IR in children &gt;12-17 years requiring an opioid to treat their acute postoperative pain of various etiologies will be assessed.</measure>
    <time_frame>From baseline up to 4 months</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
